# Creating a Unauthorized Federated Identity

## Setup

Step 1: Go to https://console.aws.amazon.com/cognito/ and select "Manage Federated Identities

Step 2: Create new identity pool, enter the name and check "Enable access to unauthenticated identities"

Step 3: View sample code to get your identity pool id (in red)

Step 4: Create XCode project and create a Podfile

Step 5: Add `pod AWSCognito` & `pod AWSCore`

Step 6: `pod install`
